  "title": "Operations Admin / Project Admin (Tuas)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $3000 to $3700 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Tuas (Company Transport provided)</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: Normal Working Hours (Mon to Fri only)</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Assist in monitoring client’s payment status, collecting receivables and finalizing project accounts for completed projects</strong></li><li>Involved in asset and inventory reconciliation</li><li><strong>Assist in preparation of monthly financial and inventory reports to management</strong></li><li>Coordinate with Sales and Marketing Department to prepare quotations</li><li><strong>Assist in project delivery by receiving client’s purchase orders, issuing delivery orders and return forms, arranging for equipment testing and maintenance, responding to client’s requests where necessary</strong></li><li>Assist in preparation of progress claims and invoices, and verifying details with clients</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties when required or as instructed</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>O Level / Diploma or equivalent qualifications</li><li><strong>Proficiency in Microsoft Word and Microsoft Excel</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
